There have been so many posts on CD and other forums about teams saying their radio won’t connect, that are actually caused by not setting the team number after imaging their roborio. The team number must be set after reimaging the roborio 2; the number will not be stored across images, and the sd card flashing method will not set it.

Follow the link below for how to do this.

FIRST Robotics Competition Documentation

roboRIO Team Number Setter

roboRIO Team Number Setter tool. The roboRIO Team Number Setter is a cross-platform utility that can be used to set the team number on the roboRIO. It is an alternative to the roboRIO imaging tool ...
